<div class="row" style="min-height:100vh">

  <div class="col-12" style="background-color:#202a3c">
    
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="height: 100%;">
      <div class="card" style="width: 70%; height:560px; background-color:#303030; border:2px solid #F5F5F5;">
        <div class="card-header d-flex justify-content-center mt-1" style="border-bottom:2px solid #F5F5F5;">
          <h5 style="color:#F5F5F5;">Account Login</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-row" style="height: 460px;">
          <div style="width: 40%">
            <div class="card" style="height: 20rem; width: 18rem; background-color:#303030; border-style:none;">
              <img src="https://i.imgur.com/eXuEAFv.png">
              <div class="card-body">
                <p class="card-text" style="color:#CFCFCF; font-size:18px;">「No water, no life. <br> &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;No blue, no green。」
                </p>
                <p class="card-text text-end me-2" style="color:#CFCFCF; font-size:16px;"> - Sylvia Earle
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body d-flex align-items-center" style="width: 60%; height: 450px;">
            <form class="form-signin" action="/login" method="POST" style="width: 100%;">
              <div class="form-row mb-3">
                <label class="form-label" style="color:#D4D4D4;" for="email">信箱</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Email" required
                  value="{{ email }}">
              </div>
              <div class="form-row mb-3 mt-3">
                <label class="form-label" style="color:#D4D4D4;" for="password">密碼</label>
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Password" required>
    
              </div>
              <div class="mt-5 d-flex align-items-end" style="height:100px;">
                <button class="btn btn-outline-light btn-block" type="submit">登入</button>
              </div>
    
            </form>

            
          </div>
          
        </div>
        <div class="me-1 text-end">
          <p class="me-3"style="color:#CFCFCF; font-size:16px;">還沒有帳號嗎？&nbsp; <a href="/register"
              style="color:#CFCFCF;text-decoration:none;font-size:16px;">點我註冊</a></p>
        </div>


  </div>



</div>





  </div>
</div>